        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2071428423" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6537861541380136369">When The Reaper Comes is a riveting novel following former Navy SEAL Adam as he visits his hometown, friends and family. Adam&apos;s current job is in security, and he&apos;s given his next assignment close to home--to protect a rock star who&apos;s made an enemy of ISIS, and is performing nearby. Adam and his partner work alongside his friends in the police and the NSA to find the terrorists and stop them before the damage is done! The novel is exciting and fast paced, keeping you on the edge of your seat unt</span>
  <span id="freeText6537861541380136369" style="display:none">When The Reaper Comes is a riveting novel following former Navy SEAL Adam as he visits his hometown, friends and family. Adam's current job is in security, and he's given his next assignment close to home--to protect a rock star who's made an enemy of ISIS, and is performing nearby. Adam and his partner work alongside his friends in the police and the NSA to find the terrorists and stop them before the damage is done! The novel is exciting and fast paced, keeping you on the edge of your seat until the very end.</span>
